OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain or
OL,6,Fheavy showers soon clearing into the
OL,7,Fevening with clear spells developing.
OL,8,FCloud then thickens again from the
OL,9,Fwest after midnight, with further
OL,10,Fshowers possible, which could be
OL,11,Fheavy. Breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FBreezy start with a mixture
OL,14,Fof sunny spells and showers,
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy. Winds will ease
OL,16,Fthrough the day, with showers also
OL,17,Ffading into the evening. Cooler than
OL,18,Fon Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
