OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLight
OL,6,Frain clearing Friday morning. Staying
OL,7,Fcloudy before further rain,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy, spreads east later
OL,9,Fin the day. Sunny spells and showers
OL,10,FSaturday. Drier and sunnier with winds
OL,11,Feasing Sunday.
